Events.title: Events
Events.description: When the state of a resource changes, a new event resource is created to record the change. When an event is created, this event is stored in the database in the stored_event table and is also sent to a rabbitMq queue.

Introduction.title: Introduction
Introduction.description: The purpose of this test is to implement a RESTful API to manage the list of the characters present on Game of Thrones, paying special attention to the use of best practices, following SOLID and Clean Code principles.

UsedTechnology.title: Used technology
UsedTechnology.description: This is a service that is accessed through a web server using nginx, exposing port 8080 to make requests.
